SAMPLE LIBRARY EXCLUSION
================================================================================

IMPORTANT: The Larry Seyer Acoustic Drum Library (audio sample files in FLAC
format and their associated SFZ mapping files) included with official Sirius
Looper distributions is NOT covered by this license.

The Larry Seyer Acoustic Drum Library is proprietary content:
Copyright (C) 1999 Larry Seyer. All Rights Reserved.

Sirius Looper ships with a selection from this library, played by an embedded
sampler engine derived from the sister application OTTO. The selection is
smaller than the library distributed with OTTO, but is governed by the same
terms. See SAMPLE-LICENSE.md for the terms governing use of the drum sample
library.

The AGPLv3 license applies only to the Sirius Looper software source code, not
to any bundled audio content or sample libraries.

